#: addons/Down_the_Mountain.wad/addon:4 input:8 input:9 input:10 standard
msgid "Down the Mountain"
msgstr "Down the Mountain"

#: addons/Down_the_Mountain.wad/addon:5 input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"The legend says: ''When ever one goes down our mountain, he never comes "
"back''. As time goes by, legends become old legends and then they will "
"become myths. But each time has his own hero who wants to proof old myths... "
"Good luck, hero, see if the old legend is a myth or a truth..."
msgstr ""
"The legend says: ''When ever one goes down our mountain, he never comes "
"back''. As time goes by, legends become old legends and then they will "
"become myths. But each time has his own hero who wants to proof old myths... "
"Good luck, hero, see if the old legend is a myth or a truth..."

